Steps 2,500 Steps {stepsProgress}% of your goals Future Feature Activity Progress Thomas Fletcher Sydney, Australia Your Goals Running: 70km/80km Weight Loss: 70kg/100kg Monthly Progress Scheduled Training - Yoga Class 22 Mar Training - Swimming 22 Mar ); }; export default HomePage;
